reviewText: Ricky Sprocket "Showbiz Boy"  is one of the coolest most greatest cartoons from Nicktoons that's what I think. On this DVD the picture quality is great! The Aspect Ratio is 1.77:1 come on that has to be good. This is a Have to BUY! DVD also the casing for this DVD is colorful & detailed even the disc.
Ricky Sprocket is great got dvd when it stopped airing on nicktoons in march 2010
